                  </hi>. These half-sovereigns are both bad.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">The prisoner in his defence stated that he picked up a sovereign in Red Lion Street, and went into a public-house to change it, and somebody standing in front of lie bar gave him the two half-sovereigns for it.</hi> 
